latestPosts.caption:
🍭 Propaganda We’re Not Falling For 🍭
1️⃣ “Healthier candy has no flavor.”
 Newsflash: Real fruit + juicy chew = 🍓 explosion in every bite.

2️⃣ “Candy and clean ingredients can’t coexist.”
 We beg to differ. No weird stuff. Ever.

3️⃣ “You can’t be nostalgic and grown-up at the same time.”
 Tell that to your 10-year-old self who would probably vouch for our dreamy fruit chews.

4️⃣ “Vegan treats are just sad substitutes.”
 Ours are 100% vegan, 100% delicious, and 100% worthy of a double-take.

5️⃣ “Candy can’t spark joy and be better-for-you.”
 Challenge accepted. Sweet bursts of flavor, zero guilt. #CandyRevolution

We’re here to prove that clean, joyful candy isn’t a myth... it’s Sweet Haven. 🍬✨

Ready to see the propaganda crumble? You can find us at @JewelOsco, SproutsMarket & @Instacart!

#SweetHaven #PropagandaProof #BetterCandy #RealFruitRealJoy #CandyUnfiltered

latestPosts.caption:
Chewy. Stretchy. Ridiculously satisfying. We love celebrating these qualities of Sweet Haven!

And now, we have a whole holiday to do just that. For #NationalTaffyDay, we’re giving major props to the chew. Sweet Haven hits just right; with no gelatin, no corn syrup, and no compromises.

With Peach, Mango, Watermelon, Blueberry, Tart Berry, and Wild Berry flavors, you can’t go wrong.

Drop your favorite flavor in the comments 🍑 🥭 🍉🍓🫐

Let’s hear it for the real MVPs: bees. 🐝💛
Without them, there’d be no juicy berries, no peachy bliss, no juicy watermelons, no Sweet Haven.

On World Bee Day, we’re honoring pollinators that keep flavor alive for natural products like ours.

#WorldBeeDay #MadeWithFruit #SweetHavenNatural
